  "title": "[Gov Healthcare] 1 Year Contract Operations Executive - UP$5500 (Surgery Team/ Central) #HCY",
  "description": "<p><strong>Challenges </strong></p><p>You will provide operational support to clinical departments and work closely with key stakeholders on matters related to implementation and monitoring of projects, process improvement, justification for new services and funding, and ensure that they are in line with the hospital's overall strategic direction. You will assume a key role in ensuring good financial performance and smooth operations of the clinical departments by proactive tracking, monitoring, analysis and reporting of key performance indicators.</p><p><strong>Requirements </strong></p><p>Bachelor degree in any discipline , preferably in hospital operations, will be advantageous </p><p>Critical thinker, self-motivated, excellent communication skills, a team player who is also able to work independently </p><p>Proficient in MS Office<br /></p><p>For interested candidates, please send your most recent and updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:recruithealthcare@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>sallytsin@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>WA me at <a href=\"http://wa.me/+6598326219\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://wa.me/+6598326219</a> or tele me at @sallytsin</p><p>Tsin Chien Yee Sally<br />R25127272<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd <br />EA License No. 99C4599</p>",
